# HTMX Template Pattern

```html
{% extends "base.html" %}
{% block content %}
<div id="content" hx-get="{% url 'partial-view' %}" hx-trigger="load" hx-swap="innerHTML">
  <div class="animate-pulse">Loading...</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
```

**Rules:**
- Prefix partial templates with `_` (e.g., `_table.html`, `_modal.html`)
- Partials are swapped via HTMX `hx-swap` attribute
- Use `hx-target` to specify swap target
